{
  "video_id": "YXWKuK-Qsu4",
  "title": "How college loans exploit students for profit | Sajay Samuel",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12975.0,
      "end_time": 18435.0,
      "text": "Today 40 million Americans are indebted for their passage to the new economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 20390.0,
      "end_time": 22143.0,
      "text": "Too poor to pay their way through college,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22167.0,
      "end_time": 26509.0,
      "text": "they now owe lenders more than one trillion US dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 27709.0,
      "end_time": 29948.0,
      "text": "They do find what jobs they can get"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 29972.0,
      "end_time": 32457.0,
      "text": "to pay off a debt that is secured on their person."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 33201.0,
      "end_time": 35249.0,
      "text": "In America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35273.0,
      "end_time": 40804.0,
      "text": "even a bankrupt gambler gets a second chance."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 42351.0,
      "end_time": 45153.0,
      "text": "But it is nearly impossible"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 45177.0,
      "end_time": 48652.0,
      "text": "for an American to get discharged their student loan debts."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 52421.0,
      "end_time": 55141.0,
      "text": "Once upon a time in America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 55165.0,
      "end_time": 57815.0,
      "text": "going to college did not mean graduating with debt."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 59299.0,
      "end_time": 64584.0,
      "text": "My friend Paul&#39;s father graduated from Colorado State University"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 64608.00000000001,
      "end_time": 65759.0,
      "text": "on the GI Bill."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 67546.0,
      "end_time": 69134.0,
      "text": "For his generation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 69158.0,
      "end_time": 72600.0,
      "text": "higher education was free or almost free,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 72300.0,
      "end_time": 74427.0,
      "text": "because it was thought of as a public good."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 75676.0,
      "end_time": 76872.0,
      "text": "Not anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 78171.0,
      "end_time": 82267.0,
      "text": "When Paul also graduated from Colorado State University,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 82291.0,
      "end_time": 85664.0,
      "text": "he paid for his English degree by working part-time."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 86164.0,
      "end_time": 87315.0,
      "text": "30 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 87339.0,
      "end_time": 90600.0,
      "text": "higher education tuition was affordable, reasonable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 90300.0,
      "end_time": 93426.0,
      "text": "and what debts you accumulated, you paid off by graduation date."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 93952.0,
      "end_time": 95102.0,
      "text": "Not anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 95829.0,
      "end_time": 99202.0,
      "text": "Paul&#39;s daughter followed in his footsteps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 99227.0,
      "end_time": 100528.0,
      "text": "but with one difference:"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 100552.0,
      "end_time": 103440.0,
      "text": "when she graduated five years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 103680.0,
      "end_time": 104417.0,
      "text": "it was with a whopping debt."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 105179.0,
      "end_time": 108521.0,
      "text": "Students like Kate have to take on a loan"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 108545.0,
      "end_time": 111744.0,
      "text": "because the cost of higher education has become unaffordable"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 111768.0,
      "end_time": 115457.0,
      "text": "for many if not most American families."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 116427.0,
      "end_time": 117577.0,
      "text": "But so what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 118117.0,
      "end_time": 120665.0,
      "text": "Getting into debt to buy an expensive education"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 120689.0,
      "end_time": 123451.0,
      "text": "is not all bad if you could pay it off"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 123475.0,
      "end_time": 126609.0,
      "text": "with the increased income that you earned from it."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 127266.0,
      "end_time": 129379.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s where the rubber meets the road."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 131652.0,
      "end_time": 137248.0,
      "text": "Even a college grad earned 10 percent more in 2001"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 137272.0,
      "end_time": 139247.0,
      "text": "than she did in 2013."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 139984.0,
      "end_time": 141134.0,
      "text": "So ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 141779.0,
      "end_time": 143438.0,
      "text": "tuition costs up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 143462.0,
      "end_time": 144984.0,
      "text": "public funding down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 145900.0,
      "end_time": 147446.0,
      "text": "family incomes diminished,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 147470.0,
      "end_time": 149882.0,
      "text": "personal incomes weak."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 150241.0,
      "end_time": 154646.0,
      "text": "Is it any wonder that more than a quarter of those who must"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 154670.0,
      "end_time": 156677.0,
      "text": "cannot make their student loan payments?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 158852.0,
      "end_time": 161829.0,
      "text": "The worst of times can be the best of times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 161853.0,
      "end_time": 165731.0,
      "text": "because certain truths flash up in ways that you can&#39;t ignore."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 166446.0,
      "end_time": 168392.0,
      "text": "I want to speak of three of them today."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 169571.0,
      "end_time": 173445.0,
      "text": "1.2 trillion dollars of debts for diplomas"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 173469.0,
      "end_time": 175934.0,
      "text": "make it abundantly obvious"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 175958.0,
      "end_time": 179696.0,
      "text": "that higher education is a consumer product you can buy."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 180283.0,
      "end_time": 185101.0,
      "text": "All of us talk about education just as the economists do now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 185125.0,
      "end_time": 189606.0,
      "text": "as an investment that you make to improve the human stock"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 189630.0,
      "end_time": 191371.0,
      "text": "by training them for work."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 191812.0,
      "end_time": 196535.0,
      "text": "As an investment you make to sort and classify people"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 196559.0,
      "end_time": 199327.0,
      "text": "so that employers can hire them more easily."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 200396.0,
      "end_time": 203793.0,
      "text": "The U.S. News & World Report ranks colleges"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 203818.0,
      "end_time": 207710.0,
      "text": "just as the consumer report rates washing machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 207950.0,
      "end_time": 210858.0,
      "text": "The language is peppered with barbarisms."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 210882.0,
      "end_time": 214263.0,
      "text": "Teachers are called \"service providers,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 214287.0,
      "end_time": 216400.0,
      "text": "students are called \"consumers.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 217509.0,
      "end_time": 221390.0,
      "text": "Sociology and Shakespeare and soccer and science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 221414.0,
      "end_time": 223900.0,
      "text": "all of these are \"content.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 225318.0,
      "end_time": 226699.0,
      "text": "Student debt is profitable."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 226723.0,
      "end_time": 227873.0,
      "text": "Only not on you."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 229961.0,
      "end_time": 233564.0,
      "text": "Your debt fattens the profit of the student loan industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 234400.0,
      "end_time": 236477.0,
      "text": "The two 800-pound gorillas of which --"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 236501.0,
      "end_time": 238564.0,
      "text": "Sallie Mae and Navient --"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 238588.0,
      "end_time": 243793.0,
      "text": "posted last year a combined profit of 1.2 billion dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 244568.0,
      "end_time": 247140.0,
      "text": "And just like home mortgages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 247164.0,
      "end_time": 250350.0,
      "text": "student loans can be bundled and packaged and sliced and diced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 250374.0,
      "end_time": 251624.0,
      "text": "and sold on Wall Street."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 252369.0,
      "end_time": 253965.0,
      "text": "And colleges and universities"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 253989.0,
      "end_time": 257289.0,
      "text": "that invest in these securitized loans"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 258170.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259321.00000000003,
      "text": "profit twice."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 259735.0,
      "end_time": 261156.0,
      "text": "Once from your tuition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 261180.0,
      "end_time": 263560.0,
      "text": "and then again from the interest on debt."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 265108.0,
      "end_time": 267474.0,
      "text": "With all that money to be made,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 267498.0,
      "end_time": 273850.0,
      "text": "are we surprised that some in the higher education business"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 273109.0,
      "end_time": 275181.0,
      "text": "have begun to engage in false advertising,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 275205.0,
      "end_time": 276361.0,
      "text": "in bait and switch ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 278585.0,
      "end_time": 282680.0,
      "text": "in exploiting the very ignorance that they pretend to educate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 284144.0,
      "end_time": 285294.0,
      "text": "Third:"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 285678.0,
      "end_time": 287670.0,
      "text": "diplomas are a brand."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 287741.0,
      "end_time": 290920.0,
      "text": "Many years ago my teacher wrote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 290116.0,
      "end_time": 292657.0,
      "text": "\"When students are treated as consumers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 292681.0,
      "end_time": 295806.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re made prisoners of addiction and envy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 299794.0,
      "end_time": 304335.0,
      "text": "Just as consumers can be sold and resold upgraded versions of an iPhone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 304359.0,
      "end_time": 307301.0,
      "text": "so also people can be sold more and more education."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 308807.0,
      "end_time": 310673.0,
      "text": "College is the new high school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 310697.0,
      "end_time": 312210.0,
      "text": "we already say that."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 313408.0,
      "end_time": 314807.0,
      "text": "But why stop there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 314831.0,
      "end_time": 318308.0,
      "text": "People can be upsold on certifications and recertifications,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 318332.0,
      "end_time": 320688.0,
      "text": "master&#39;s degrees, doctoral degrees."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 323436.0,
      "end_time": 327149.0,
      "text": "Higher education is also marketed as a status object."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 328634.0,
      "end_time": 329785.0,
      "text": "Buy a degree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 329809.0,
      "end_time": 332996.0,
      "text": "much like you do a Lexus of a Louis Vuitton bag,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 333200.0,
      "end_time": 334813.0,
      "text": "to distinguish yourself from others."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 334838.0,
      "end_time": 337289.0,
      "text": "So you can be the object of envy of others."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 338669.0,
      "end_time": 340400.0,
      "text": "Diplomas are a brand."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 341340.0,
      "end_time": 347629.0,
      "text": "But these truths are often times hidden by a very noisy sales pitch."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 348535.0,
      "end_time": 350171.0,
      "text": "There is not a day that goes by"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 350195.0,
      "end_time": 355232.0,
      "text": "without some policy guy on television telling us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 355256.0,
      "end_time": 357280.0,
      "text": "\"A college degree is absolutely essential"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 357304.0,
      "end_time": 360200.0,
      "text": "to get on that up escalator to a middle-class life.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 360890.0,
      "end_time": 364568.0,
      "text": "And the usual evidence offered is the college premium:"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 364592.0,
      "end_time": 369839.0,
      "text": "a college grad who makes on average 56 percent more than a high school grad."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 370425.0,
      "end_time": 372473.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s look at that number more carefully,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 372497.0,
      "end_time": 373823.0,
      "text": "because on the face of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 373847.0,
      "end_time": 377191.0,
      "text": "it seems to belie the stories we all hear"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 377215.0,
      "end_time": 381602.0,
      "text": "about college grads working as baristas and cashiers."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 382545.0,
      "end_time": 387696.0,
      "text": "Of 100 people who enroll in any form of post-secondary education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 387720.0,
      "end_time": 390768.0,
      "text": "45 do not complete it in a timely fashion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 390792.0,
      "end_time": 393857.0,
      "text": "for a number of reasons, including financial."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 394275.0,
      "end_time": 396188.0,
      "text": "Of the 55 that do graduate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 396212.0,
      "end_time": 398260.0,
      "text": "two will remain unemployed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 398284.0,
      "end_time": 401140.0,
      "text": "and another 18 are underemployed."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 402580.0,
      "end_time": 405733.0,
      "text": "So, college grads earn more than high school grads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 405757.0,
      "end_time": 408750.0,
      "text": "but does it pay for the exorbitant tuition"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 408774.0,
      "end_time": 411165.0,
      "text": "and the lost wages while at college?"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 411661.0,
      "end_time": 414257.0,
      "text": "Now even economists admit"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 414281.0,
      "end_time": 419511.0,
      "text": "going to college pays off for only those who complete it."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 420950.0,
      "end_time": 424127.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s only because high school wages have been cut to the bone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 424151.0,
      "end_time": 425591.0,
      "text": "for decades now."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 427369.0,
      "end_time": 429258.0,
      "text": "For decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 429282.0,
      "end_time": 431639.0,
      "text": "workers with a high school degree"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 431663.0,
      "end_time": 435766.0,
      "text": "have been denied a fair share of what they have produced."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 436480.0,
      "end_time": 439385.0,
      "text": "And had they received as they should have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 439409.0,
      "end_time": 443361.0,
      "text": "then going to college would have been a bad investment for many."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 443386.0,
      "end_time": 445512.0,
      "text": "College premium?"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 445941.0,
      "end_time": 447695.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s a high school discount."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 448688.0,
      "end_time": 453920.0,
      "text": "Two out of three people who enroll are not going to find an adequate job."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 453756.0,
      "end_time": 456866.0,
      "text": "And the future, for them, doesn&#39;t look particularly promising --"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 456891.0,
      "end_time": 458613.0,
      "text": "in fact, it&#39;s downright bleak."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 458637.0,
      "end_time": 461410.0,
      "text": "And it is they who are going to suffer"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 462541.0,
      "end_time": 465224.0,
      "text": "the most punishing forms of student debt."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 466200.0,
      "end_time": 467153.0,
      "text": "And it is they,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 467177.0,
      "end_time": 468558.0,
      "text": "curiously and sadly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 468582.0,
      "end_time": 472391.0,
      "text": "who are marketed most loudly about this college premium thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 473986.0,
      "end_time": 476383.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s not just cynical marketing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 476407.0,
      "end_time": 477556.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s cruel."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 479277.0,
      "end_time": 480426.0,
      "text": "So what do we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 481279.0,
      "end_time": 486888.0,
      "text": "What if students and parents treated higher education as a consumer product?"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 488199.0,
      "end_time": 489738.0,
      "text": "Everybody else seems to."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 490686.0,
      "end_time": 492948.0,
      "text": "Then, like any other consumer product,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 492972.0,
      "end_time": 495471.0,
      "text": "you would demand to know what you&#39;re paying for."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 495495.0,
      "end_time": 496710.0,
      "text": "When you buy medicines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 496734.0,
      "end_time": 498649.0,
      "text": "you get a list of side effects."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 498673.0,
      "end_time": 500785.0,
      "text": "When you buy a higher educational product,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 500809.0,
      "end_time": 502443.0,
      "text": "you should have a warning label"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 502467.0,
      "end_time": 504659.0,
      "text": "that allows consumers to choose,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 504683.0,
      "end_time": 506620.0,
      "text": "make informed choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 506838.0,
      "end_time": 508300.0,
      "text": "When you buy a car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 508540.0,
      "end_time": 510664.0,
      "text": "it tells you how many miles per gallon to expect."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 511188.0,
      "end_time": 512634.0,
      "text": "Who knows what to expect"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 512658.0,
      "end_time": 516372.0,
      "text": "from a degree say, in Canadian Studies."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 516806.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518465.00000000006,
      "text": "There is such a thing, by the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 520989.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523440.00000000006,
      "text": "What if there was an app for that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 526402.0,
      "end_time": 531270.0,
      "text": "One that linked up the cost of a major to the expected income."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 532208.0,
      "end_time": 534574.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s call it Income-Based Tuition or IBT."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 534598.0,
      "end_time": 536120.0,
      "text": "One of you make this."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 536144.0,
      "end_time": 537683.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 537707.0,
      "end_time": 539439.0,
      "text": "Discover your reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 539463.0,
      "end_time": 541771.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 541796.0,
      "end_time": 543225.0,
      "text": "There are three advantages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 543249.0,
      "end_time": 545930.0,
      "text": "three benefits to Income-Based Tuition."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 547232.0,
      "end_time": 549121.0,
      "text": "Any user can figure out"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 549145.0,
      "end_time": 552348.0,
      "text": "how much money he or she will make from a given college and major."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 553105.0,
      "end_time": 554447.0,
      "text": "Such informed users"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 554471.0,
      "end_time": 558416.0,
      "text": "are unlikely to fall victim to the huckster&#39;s ploy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 558440.0,
      "end_time": 559850.0,
      "text": "to the sales pitch."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 559874.0,
      "end_time": 561580.0,
      "text": "But also to choose wisely."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 561604.0,
      "end_time": 564600.0,
      "text": "Why would anybody pay more for college"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 564300.0,
      "end_time": 567550.0,
      "text": "than let&#39;s say, 15 percent of the additional income they earn?"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 569400.0,
      "end_time": 571756.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a second benefit to Income-Based Tuition."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 571780.0,
      "end_time": 574740.0,
      "text": "By tying the cost to the income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 574764.0,
      "end_time": 579185.0,
      "text": "college administrators would be forced to manage costs better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 579209.0,
      "end_time": 581549.0,
      "text": "to find innovative ways to do so."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 581573.0,
      "end_time": 582727.0,
      "text": "For instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 582751.0,
      "end_time": 586810.0,
      "text": "all of you students here pay roughly the same tuition for every major."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 587478.0,
      "end_time": 591525.0,
      "text": "That is manifestly unfair, and should change."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 592295.0,
      "end_time": 596216.0,
      "text": "An engineering student uses more resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 596240.0,
      "end_time": 598649.0,
      "text": "and facilities and labs and faculty"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 598673.0,
      "end_time": 600351.0,
      "text": "than a philosophy student."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 601581.0,
      "end_time": 603685.0,
      "text": "But the philosophy student, as a consequence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 603709.0,
      "end_time": 605899.0,
      "text": "is subsidizing the engineering student."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 606300.0,
      "end_time": 608991.0,
      "text": "Who then, by the way, goes on and earns more money."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 609150.0,
      "end_time": 612722.0,
      "text": "Why should two people buy the same product,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 612746.0,
      "end_time": 613920.0,
      "text": "pay the same,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 613945.0,
      "end_time": 616722.0,
      "text": "but one person receive half or a third of the service."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 618448.0,
      "end_time": 622519.0,
      "text": "In fact, college grads, some majors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 622543.0,
      "end_time": 626163.0,
      "text": "pay 25 percent of their income servicing their student debt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 626187.0,
      "end_time": 627860.0,
      "text": "while others pay five percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 629510.0,
      "end_time": 634260.0,
      "text": "That kind if inequity would end when majors are priced more correctly."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 635420.0,
      "end_time": 637201.0,
      "text": "Now of course, all this data --"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 637225.0,
      "end_time": 639299.0,
      "text": "and one of you is going to do this, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 639323.0,
      "end_time": 641170.0,
      "text": "All this data has to be well designed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 641194.0,
      "end_time": 643291.0,
      "text": "maybe audited by public accounting firms"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 643316.0,
      "end_time": 645268.0,
      "text": "to avoid statistical lies."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 645292.0,
      "end_time": 647137.0,
      "text": "We know about statistics, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 648766.0,
      "end_time": 649988.0,
      "text": "But be that as it may,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 650130.0,
      "end_time": 654394.0,
      "text": "the third and biggest benefit of Income-Based Tuition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 654418.0,
      "end_time": 659847.0,
      "text": "is it would free Americans from the fear and the fact of financial ruin"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 659871.0,
      "end_time": 662370.0,
      "text": "because they bought a defective product."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 662813.0,
      "end_time": 665132.0,
      "text": "Perhaps, in time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 665156.0,
      "end_time": 667404.0,
      "text": "young and old Americans may rediscover,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 667428.0,
      "end_time": 669625.0,
      "text": "as the gentleman said earlier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 669649.0,
      "end_time": 671688.0,
      "text": "their curiosity, their love of learning --"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 671712.0,
      "end_time": 673149.0,
      "text": "begin to study what they love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 673173.0,
      "end_time": 674352.0,
      "text": "love what they study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 674376.0,
      "end_time": 675759.0,
      "text": "follow their passion ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 676577.0,
      "end_time": 679460.0,
      "text": "getting stimulated by their intelligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 679700.0,
      "end_time": 682507.0,
      "text": "follow paths of inquiry that they really want to."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 682848.0,
      "end_time": 687298.0,
      "text": "After all, it was Eric and Kevin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 687322.0,
      "end_time": 688490.0,
      "text": "two years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 689498.0,
      "end_time": 692930.0,
      "text": "just exactly these kinds of young men,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 692954.0,
      "end_time": 694976.0,
      "text": "who prompted me and worked with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 695000.0,
      "end_time": 696561.0,
      "text": "and still do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 696585.0,
      "end_time": 700271.0,
      "text": "in the study of indebted students in America."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 701272.0,
      "end_time": 702803.0,
      "text": "Thank you for your attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 702827.0,
      "end_time": 707391.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}